Summary: Properties and their default values for the BackBufferCopy class.

- copy_mode (enum BackBufferCopy_CopyMode): Specifies the copy operation mode. Default: 1
- rect (class Rect2): Defines the area to copy. Default: Rect2(-100, -100, 200, 200)
